Actions on Task

To view actions available on the Tasks select the Action option. A list with all actions will be displayed.

The actions depend on the task state. The following states are possible:

  • Not Yet Started - Initial state of the task. The work of the task is not started yet.
  • In Process - Active state of the Task. All Tasks actions can be performed
  • On Hold - The work of the task is suspended. In this state the task can be restarted.
  • Stopped - Final state of the task. The progress on the task is stop before is normal completion
  • Completed - The Task in Completed state is inactive. Only the permissions of the Task can be edited
